  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564820/extras/2ec7b44d9def06bcf95c4e0eb2017acc.poster.avif?t=1760065266\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564820/extras/2ec7b44d9def06bcf95c4e0eb2017acc.webm?t=1760065266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564820/extras/2ec7b44d9def06bcf95c4e0eb2017acc.mp4?t=1760065266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>You have nothing, and you're alone...</strong><br>You're on a different yet very familiar looking planet completely alone with nothing but your bare hands. Utilize the resources in your local area that the planet has to offer to your advantage! Craft tools and weapons, fight enemies, and build a base!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564820/extras/0c80360ab7aced60eaecee4b46874840.poster.avif?t=1760065266\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564820/extras/0c80360ab7aced60eaecee4b46874840.webm?t=1760065266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564820/extras/0c80360ab7aced60eaecee4b46874840.mp4?t=1760065266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>What lies below the surface?</strong><br>Delve deeper, explore the depths, and find hidden treasure! There are hundreds of layers of caves to explore, but watch out for increasing danger the deeper you go!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564820/extras/8c13b2c9c5df489096f74d44df7a07d1.poster.avif?t=1760065266\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564820/extras/8c13b2c9c5df489096f74d44df7a07d1.webm?t=1760065266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564820/extras/8c13b2c9c5df489096f74d44df7a07d1.mp4?t=1760065266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Science!</strong><br>Research new technologies, and learn new crafting recipes by doing science! The more science you do, the more capabilities the player has on areas such as crafting, fighting, and survival!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564820/extras/3c41d5af740280e263172ef7bed210cf.poster.avif?t=1760065266\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564820/extras/3c41d5af740280e263172ef7bed210cf.webm?t=1760065266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564820/extras/3c41d5af740280e263172ef7bed210cf.mp4?t=1760065266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Let's go planet exploiting!</strong><br>Exploit other planets, scout new planetary landing sites, and continue doing science to research your way towards automating the gathering of certain resources!<br><br><strong>Note:</strong><br>This game is singleplayer only, and will remain singleplayer for the foreseeable future.",
